Name: DevelopmentResultsName
Description: A name for the DevelopmentResults. May be expressed in multiple languages. Repeat the element to express names with different content, for example different names for different systems.

Name: Label
Description: A display label for the Development Results. Supports multiple language versions of the same content as well as optional formatting of the content. Repeat for labels with different content, for example, labels with differing length limitations.

Name: Description
Description: A description of the overall Development Results. Supports multiple language versions of the same content as well as optional formatting of the content.

Name: DevelopmentPlanReference
Description: References the Development Plan which the results refer to.

Name: DevelopmentProcessReference
Description: References the Development Process which the results refer to.

Name: ResultsDate
Description: The date or date range of obtaining results from the development work.

Name: ResultDetail
Description: Details of specific results of the development plan and process. May refer to specific development activities or DevelopmentSteps within a DevelopmentProcess.
